  <brief_title>Small Airway Obstruction in Asthma, COPD, ACOS</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Study on Sputum Anti-inflammatory Mediators in Patients With Asthma or Asthma and COPD Overlap (ACOS) Syndrome, and COPD</official_title>
  <sponsors>
